Package: openbrowser
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: A GNOME-style web browser
 OpenBrowser is a fast, private, and feature-rich web browser built
 with GTK4 and WebKitGTK. It features a modern GNOME-style interface
 with gray color scheme, multi-tab browsing, built-in ad blocker,
 tracker protection, download manager, bookmark manager, history,
 developer tools, and extensive keyboard shortcuts.
